description.en: Ethereum Vault is a next generation coin of Ethereum Crypto Currency. Ethereum Vault started from August 8, 2020 Warsaw Poland. We are team having extensive coin market cryptocurrency experience of 5 years. Our aim is to make Ethereum Vault a publics currency made popular by peoples choice. Ethereum Vault becoming the coin of people to do transction in exchanges and public sector. With the peoples support, we have started Ethereum Vault with 0.013 USD and within 2 years time it reached to 10 USD. It can be trade (Buy/ Sale) on vindax.com exchange with ETHV_ETH and ETHV_BTC
